quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,aur un ke aamaal ki buraiyan un par zahir ho jaien gi aur jis ( azaab ) ki woh hansi uratye they woh un ko aaghire ga
  45,34,aur kaha jaye ga ke jis terhan tum ne is din ke anay ko bhala rakha tha. isi terhan aaj hum tumhe bhala den ge aur tumhara thikana dozakh hai aur koi tumhara madadgaar nahi
  45,35,yeh is liye ke tum ne khuda ki aayton ko mkhol bana rakha tha aur duniya ki zindagi ne tum ko dhokay mein daal rakha tha. so aaj yeh log nah dozakh se nikalay jayen ge aur nah un ki tauba qubool ki jaye gi
  45,36,pas khuda hi ko har terhan ki tareef ( sazawar ) hai jo asmano ka maalik aur zameen ka maalik aur tamam Jahan ka perwar-digaar hai
  45,37,aur asmano aur zameen mein usi ke liye barayi hai. aur woh ghalib aur Dana hai
  46,1,Haa-Meeem
  46,2,( yeh ) kitaab khuday-e ghalib ( aur ) hikmat walay ki taraf se nazil hui hai
  46,3,hum ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo kuch un dono mein hai mabni bar hikmat aur aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye pedakiya hai. aur kafiroon ko jis cheez ki nasiyaat ki jati hai is se munh phair letay hain
  46,4,kaho ke bhala tum ne un cheezon ko dekha hai jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho ( zara ) mujhe bhi to dikhao ke unhon ne zameen mein kon si cheez peda ki hai. ya asmano mein un ki shirkat hai. agar sachey ho to is se pehlay ki koi kitaab mere paas lao. ya ilm ( anbia mein ) se kuch ( manqool ) chala aata ho ( to usay paish karo )
  46,5,aur is shakhs se barh kar kon gumraah ho sakta hai jo aisay ko pukare jo qayamat taq usay jawab nah day sakay aur un ko un ke pukarnay hi ki khabar nah ho
